Building a docker:- sudo docker build -t mohan .

Add docker to sudo
sudo groupadd docker
sudo usermod -aG docker $USER

docker run -ti -v Music_ex/Tender:~/Music_exx/Tender mohan


gcloud compute instances start example-instance
gcloud compute instances stop example-instance-1

activate environment in bash script
source <absolute_path>/activate

Check if you have any directories in your current path! You can check that by "ls -lrt" which lists the files and directories in your current path.